      <title>Meta即将到来的$ 1,000+智能眼镜将如何工作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/how-meta-s-upcoming-1000-smart-glasses-with-a-screen-will-work</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc.，加强了其流行智能眼镜的豪华版本的工作，计划包括手持控制和显示照片和应用程序的屏幕。]]></description>
